You take pride in owning &amp;amp; maintaining what your team builds.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You believe in building both teams and products that scale. You care about setting up healthy distributed teams and collaborative environments.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We operate in a nascent, rapidly evolving industry. The projects you&#39;ll end up leading sometimes demand knowledge of early, niche, and/or experimental tech, and in many cases, demand that we create such tech ourselves. You get excited by such challenges.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
