&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;10+ years of relevant compliance, risk management, legal or HR/L&amp;amp;D experience, preferably with a strong focus on creating and delivering compliance training and communications in a regulated environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
