&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent influencing and intrapersonal skills with the ability to work independently and efficiently in a hyper growth environment, together with a positive attitude and strong work ethic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
